## **Banco de Dados** 

Banco de dados: Supabase

\-- WARNING: This schema is for context only and is not meant to be run.  
\-- Table order and constraints may not be valid for execution.

CREATE TABLE public.clientes (  
  id\_cliente bigint NOT NULL,  
  Cliente text NOT NULL,  
  Razao\_social text NOT NULL,  
  Cidade text NOT NULL,  
  Vendedor text NOT NULL,  
  Limite integer NOT NULL,  
  data\_ultima\_compra date,  
  ultima\_interacao timestamp with time zone,  
  id\_vendedor bigint,  
  CONSTRAINT clientes\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id\_cliente),  
  CONSTRAINT clientes\_id\_vendedor\_fkey FOREIGN KEY (id\_vendedor) REFERENCES public.vendedores(id)  
);  
CREATE TABLE public.contatos\_cliente (  
  id\_contato bigint NOT NULL DEFAULT nextval('contatos\_cliente\_id\_contato\_seq'::regclass),  
  id\_cliente bigint NOT NULL,  
  nome\_contato text NOT NULL,  
  funcao character varying,  
  telefone character varying,  
  criado\_em timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now(),  
  CONSTRAINT contatos\_cliente\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id\_contato),  
  CONSTRAINT contatos\_cliente\_id\_cliente\_fkey FOREIGN KEY (id\_cliente) REFERENCES public.clientes(id\_cliente)  
);  
CREATE TABLE public.envios (  
  id\_envio bigint GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY NOT NULL,  
  id\_cliente bigint NOT NULL,  
  id\_mensagem bigint,  
  data\_envio date,  
  status\_entrega character varying,  
  wa\_message\_id text UNIQUE,  
  to\_phone text,  
  created\_at timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now(),  
  error\_message text,  
  id\_contato bigint,  
  CONSTRAINT envios\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id\_envio),  
  CONSTRAINT ENVIOS\_id\_mensagem\_fkey FOREIGN KEY (id\_mensagem) REFERENCES public.mensagens(id\_mensagem),  
  CONSTRAINT envios\_id\_cliente\_fkey FOREIGN KEY (id\_cliente) REFERENCES public.clientes(id\_cliente),  
  CONSTRAINT envios\_id\_contato\_fkey FOREIGN KEY (id\_contato) REFERENCES public.contatos\_cliente(id\_contato)  
);  
CREATE TABLE public.mensagens (  
  id\_mensagem bigint GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY NOT NULL,  
  created\_at timestamp with time zone NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),  
  titulo character varying,  
  texto text,  
  imagem text,  
  categoria character varying,  
  status character varying,  
  CONSTRAINT mensagens\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id\_mensagem)  
);  
CREATE TABLE public.vendedores (  
  id bigint GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY NOT NULL,  
  created\_at timestamp with time zone NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),  
  nome\_vendedor character varying NOT NULL DEFAULT ''::character varying UNIQUE,  
  CONSTRAINT vendedores\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id)  
);  
CREATE TABLE public.webhook\_logs (  
  id uuid NOT NULL DEFAULT gen\_random\_uuid(),  
  created\_at timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now(),  
  raw jsonb NOT NULL,  
  CONSTRAINT webhook\_logs\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id)  
);
